These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, drawing, reading
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, daffodil, aconite
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growspoppy##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
3. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##8
4. the person who growspoppy is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| Flower   | zinnia | daffodil   | aconite  | poppy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
City: marseilles, rome, paris, prague
1. the person traveling to prague is not to the left of the person traveling to prague##8
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
3. the person eating grapes is the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapes and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person traveling to marseilles##7
6. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
7. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| City    | paris      | prague | marseilles | rome |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, drawing, sudoku, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks | drawing | sudoku     | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

