.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, go, chess
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
3. the person playing go is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the person playing go##8
5. the fan of blues is the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| Game         | billiard | chess | go | mah-jongg |

