.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, skiing, climbing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Sport   | skiing   | rugby         | climbing | golf |

