.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
City: boston, nizza, paris, london
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person traveling to london and the person who's sport is rowing##7
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
6. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| City   | nizza      | paris | boston | london   |
| Sport      | badminton | rowing | volleyball  | cricket |

