.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, entrepreneur, project-manager
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, turtle, snake, bird
1. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the snake is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the dressmaker##7
5. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the project-manager##8
6. the project-manager is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig   | snake        | bird          | turtle |

