.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, sailing, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the person who's sport is golf##2
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
5. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the fan of indie is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Sport     | water-polo | sailing       | golf  | ice-hockey    |

