1. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person who growsmarigold##8
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbellflower##5
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Flower    | marigold        | bellflower | amaryllis      | daisy    |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | filmmaking | reading |

