1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person playing bridge##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | bridge         | domino    | poker       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

