2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person playing monopoly##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing snooker and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk | tea        | sprite       |
| Game      | monopoly | snooker  | mah-jongg | backgammon |

