.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, weightlifting, rowing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Sport   | cricket | volleyball  | rowing     | weightlifting    |

