3. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
