2. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
6. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | cat  | snake | fish  | rabbit  |
| Beverage   | water | almond-milk   | iced-tea | 7up |

