.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, green, ebony, pink
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person driving the jet-ski is not the person who likes light-blue##6
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person who likes pink is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
4. the person who likes ebony is the person driving the car##1
5. the person who likes pink is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the car##7
6. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the van and the person who likes ebony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color         | green    | pink | light-blue | ebony |
| Transport   | jet-ski | van      | subway     | car     |

 